Hi everyone,
Secret Cuts is meant to be a series of shorter comics where I can experiment more freely with different universes and styles. Each volume is completely standalone and can be seen as a creative sandbox, allowing me to try new things without committing to a 250-page comic.

If you would like immediate access to the next Secret Cuts volume or early access to the rest of my work, feel free to join me on SubscribeStar.

And if you want to keep up with my kinky projects, you can follow me here: https://x.com/SAX__kun
Or, if you want to support my work, you can join me on SubscribeStar: https://subscribestar.adult/sax_kun ❤️
